        <label>Fig. 1.</label>
        <caption>
          <p>Architecture of CLARIE. (<bold>a</bold>) CLAIREâs framework. Cells of multiple batches are projecting into a batch-corrected latent space in two stages. (<bold>b</bold>) Our proposed construction strategy for positive pairs, corresponding to the <bold>generator</bold> in (a). (<bold>c</bold>) Our proposed refinement strategy, corresponding to the <bold>filter</bold> in (a)</p>
        </caption>
        <graphic xlink:href="btad099f1" position="float"/>
